abilities.name: Mana Break
abilities.description: Burns an opponent's mana on each attack.  Mana Break deals 50% of the mana burned as damage to the target.

abilities.name: Blink
abilities.description: Short distance teleportation that allows Anti-Mage to move in and out of combat.

abilities.name: Counterspell
abilities.description: Passively grants you magic resistance. Can be activated to create an anti-magic shell around you that sends any targeted spells back towards enemies instead of affecting you.

abilities.name: Mana Void
abilities.description: For each point of mana missing by the target unit, damage is dealt to it and surrounding enemies.  The main target is also mini-stunned.

talents.name: Blink Uncontrollable Illusion
talents.description: After blinking, an uncontrollable illusion is created at Anti-Mage's original location.  Deals 25%% damage, takes 250%% damage, and lasts 10 seconds.

abilities.name: Berserker's Call
abilities.description: Axe taunts nearby enemy units, forcing them to attack him, while he gains bonus armor during the duration.

abilities.name: Battle Hunger
abilities.description: Enrages an enemy unit, causing it to be slowed and take damage over time until it kills another unit or the duration ends. Axe gains movement speed for each unit affected with Battle Hunger. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Counter Helix
abilities.description: When attacked, Axe performs a helix counter attack, dealing pure damage to all nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Culling Blade
abilities.description: Axe spots a weakness and strikes, instantly killing an enemy unit with low health, or dealing moderate damage otherwise. When an enemy hero is killed with Culling Blade, its cooldown is reset, and Axe and nearby allied units gain bonus movement speed.

talents.name: Attacking Procs Counter Helix
talents.description: Your own attacks against enemy units also have a chance to trigger Counter Helix.

abilities.name: Enfeeble
abilities.description: Lower's the target's status resistance and attack speed.

abilities.name: Brain Sap
abilities.description: Feasts on the vital energies of an enemy unit, healing Bane and dealing damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Nightmare
abilities.description: Puts the target enemy or friendly Hero to sleep. Sleeping units are awakened when attacked, but the Nightmare passes to the attacking unit. Bane can attack nightmared targets freely.

abilities.name: Fiend's Grip
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Grips an enemy unit, disabling it and causing heavy damage over time, while stealing mana every 0.5 seconds based on the unit's maximum mana.

abilities.name: Nightmare End
abilities.description: Ends all ongoing Nightmares.

talents.name: Enfeeble Steals Attack Speed
talents.description: Bane gains attack speed equal to the attack speed stolen for the duration of Enfeeble.

abilities.name: Bloodrage
abilities.description: Drives a unit into a bloodthirsty rage during which a unit deals, and takes, increased damage. Units affected by Bloodrage will be healed for a percentage of the max health of any units they kill. Units affected by Bloodrage when killed will heal a percentage of their max health to their killer. If you do not get the last hit, but are within 300 AoE of the dying hero, you will take 50% of the heal.

abilities.name: Blood Rite
abilities.description: Bloodseeker baptizes an area in sacred blood. After 3 seconds the ritual completes, causing any enemies caught in the area to take damage and become silenced.

abilities.name: Thirst
abilities.description: Bloodseeker is invigorated by the wounds of his enemies, gaining bonus movement speed and attack speed whenever an enemy hero's health falls below 75%, with the bonuses increasing as their health falls further. If an enemy hero's health falls below 25%, he will also gain vision and True Sight of that hero. Bonuses stack per hero.

abilities.name: Rupture
abilities.description: Causes an enemy unit's skin to rupture. If the unit moves, it takes a percentage of current health as damage per 100 units moved.  The damage is dealt through spell immunity. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Crystal Nova
abilities.description: A burst of damaging frost slows enemy movement and attack rate in the targeted area.

abilities.name: Frostbite
abilities.description: Encases an enemy unit in ice, prohibiting movement and attack, while dealing damage over time. Lasts 10 seconds on creeps level 6 or lower.

abilities.name: Arcane Aura
abilities.description: Gives additional mana regeneration to all friendly units on the map. This bonus is increased for Crystal Maiden.

abilities.name: Freezing Field
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Surrounds Crystal Maiden with random icy explosions that slow enemies and deal massive damage. Grants bonus armor while channeling. Lasts 10 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Frost Arrows
abilities.description: Adds a freezing effect to Drow's attacks, slowing enemy movement.  Lasts 1.5 seconds on Heroes, and 7 seconds on creeps.

abilities.name: Gust
abilities.description: Releases a wave that silences and knocks back enemy units. Knockback distance is relative to how close they are to you.

abilities.name: Precision Aura
abilities.description: Adds bonus attack speed to allied, ranged Hero units based on a percentage of Drow's agility.  Affects creeps for 30 seconds when cast.

abilities.name: Marksmanship
abilities.description: Drow's experiences in battle grant her a chance to launch arrows with incredible accuracy and effectiveness. Pierces through the enemy's defenses, ignoring their armor entirely. Instantly kills creeps and deals bonus proc physical damage to heroes. This ability is disabled if there is an enemy hero within 400 range.  Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Fissure
abilities.description: Slams the ground with a mighty totem, creating an impassable ridge of stone while stunning and damaging enemy units along its line.

abilities.name: Enchant Totem
abilities.description: Empowers Earthshaker's totem, causing it to deal extra damage on the next attack. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Aftershock
abilities.description: Causes the earth to shake underfoot, adding additional damage and stuns to nearby enemy units when Earthshaker casts his abilities.

abilities.name: Echo Slam
abilities.description: Shockwaves travel through the ground, damaging enemy units.  Each enemy hit causes an echo to damage nearby units. Real heroes cause two echoes.

abilities.name: Blade Fury
abilities.description: Causes a bladestorm of destructive force around Juggernaut, rendering him immune to magic and dealing damage to nearby enemy units.  DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

abilities.name: Healing Ward
abilities.description: Summons a Healing Ward which heals all nearby allied units, based on their max health.  The Healing Ward moves at 350 movement speed after being summoned.  Lasts 25 seconds.

abilities.name: Blade Dance
abilities.description: Gives Juggernaut a chance to deal critical damage on each attack.

abilities.name: Omnislash
abilities.description: Juggernaut leaps towards the target enemy unit with an attack, and then slashes other nearby enemy units at an increased attack rate. Juggernaut is invulnerable for the duration. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Starstorm
abilities.description: Calls down a wave of meteors to damage nearby enemy units. The closest enemy unit to Mirana in a 425 radius will be struck a second time for 75% of the damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Sacred Arrow
abilities.description: Fires a long-range arrow with deadly precision, which stuns and damages the first enemy unit it strikes. The stun duration ranges from 0.01 to 5 seconds, with bonus damage up to 140 added, based on the distance the arrow travels to its target. Instantly kills the first non-ancient creep it hits.

abilities.name: Leap
abilities.description: Mirana leaps forward into battle, empowering herself with a ferocious roar that grants bonus attack and movement speed. Speed bonus lasts 2.5 seconds.

abilities.name: Moonlight Shadow
abilities.description: Turns Mirana and all allied heroes invisible. If a hero is revealed, invisibility will restore after the fade delay as long as Moonlight Shadow's duration has not expired.

talents.name: +2 Multishot Sacred Arrows
talents.description: The extra arrows are launched in a cone shape, 30 degrees to the left and right of the original arrow, and cannot hit the same target.

abilities.name: Shadowraze
abilities.description: Shadow Fiend razes the ground directly in front of him, dealing damage to enemy units in the area. Adds a stacking damage amplifier on the target that causes the enemy to take bonus Shadow Raze damage per stack.

abilities.name: Shadowraze
abilities.description: Shadow Fiend razes the ground a short distance away from him, dealing damage to enemy units in the area. Adds a stacking damage amplifier on the target that causes the enemy to take bonus Shadow Raze damage per stack.

abilities.name: Shadowraze
abilities.description: Shadow Fiend razes the ground a longer distance away from him, dealing damage to enemy units in the area. Adds a stacking damage amplifier on the target that causes the enemy to take bonus Shadow Raze damage per stack.

abilities.name: Necromastery
abilities.description: Shadow Fiend steals the soul from units he kills, gaining bonus damage. If the killed unit is a hero, he gains 12 souls.  On death, he releases half of them from bondage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Presence of the Dark Lord
abilities.description: Shadow Fiend's presence reduces the armor of nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Requiem of Souls
abilities.description: Shadow Fiend gathers his captured souls to release them as lines of demonic energy. Units near Shadow Fiend when the souls are released can be damaged by several lines of energy. Any unit damaged by Requiem of Souls will have its movement speed and attack damage reduced. Lines of energy are created for every 2 souls captured through Necromastery. Requiem of Souls is automatically cast whenever Shadow Fiend dies, regardless of its cooldown. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Spirit Lance
abilities.description: Sends a magical spirit lance to a target enemy unit that damages and slows, while summoning an illusory phantom to attack the unit. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Doppelganger
abilities.description: Phantom Lancer briefly vanishes from the battlefield. After 1 second, Phantom Lancer and any of his nearby illusions reappear at a random position within the targeted location, along with two additional doppelgangers. Extends duration of all illusions. The two added doppelgangers have different properties: one takes normal damage and deals none, while the other takes 600% damage and deals 20% damage. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

abilities.name: Phantom Rush
abilities.description: When targetting an enemy for an attack, Phantom Lancer quickly charges into range, gaining a temporary agility boost upon reaching the target. Phantom Lancer's illusions also have this ability.

abilities.name: Juxtapose
abilities.description: Phantom Lancer has a chance to fracture his presence, creating an illusion of himself. Illusions also have a chance to fracture further. Illusions created from Phantom Lancer last for 8 seconds, while illusions created from other illusions last 4 seconds.

abilities.name: Illusory Orb
abilities.description: Puck launches a magic orb that floats in a straight path, damaging enemy units along the way. At any point, Puck may teleport to the orb's location using Ethereal Jaunt.

abilities.name: Waning Rift
abilities.description: Puck releases a burst of faerie dust that deals damage and silences enemy units nearby.

abilities.name: Phase Shift
abilities.description: Puck briefly shifts into another dimension where it is immune from harm.

abilities.name: Ethereal Jaunt
abilities.description: Teleports Puck to a flying Illusory Orb.

abilities.name: Dream Coil
abilities.description: Creates a coil of volatile magic that latches onto enemy Heroes, stunning them for 0.5 seconds and damaging them.  If the enemy hero stretches the coil by moving too far away, it snaps, stunning and dealing additional damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Dream Coil Rapid Fire
talents.description: Puck instantly attacks all enemies while affected by Dream Coil, every %value% seconds.

abilities.name: Meat Hook
abilities.description: Launches a bloody hook toward a unit or location. The hook will snag the first unit it encounters, dragging the unit back to Pudge and dealing damage if it is an enemy. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Rot
abilities.description: A toxic cloud that deals intense damage and slows movement--harming not only enemy units but Pudge himself.

abilities.name: Flesh Heap
abilities.description: Gives Pudge increased health regeneration, as well as bonus strength that increases each time Pudge kills an enemy Hero or it dies in his vicinity.  Flesh Heap is retroactive, meaning it can gain charges before it is skilled, which then become active.

abilities.name: Dismember
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Pudge chows down on an enemy unit, disabling it and dealing damage over time. Pudge gets healed for the same amount he damages. Lasts 3 seconds on Heroes, 6 seconds on creeps.

abilities.name: Plasma Field
abilities.description: Releases a wave of energetic plasma that grows in power as it expands, but also zaps on contraction, slowing and dealing damage to enemy units caught in its path. Damage and slow increases with distance from Razor. The Plasma Field hits each unit twice, once each direction.

abilities.name: Static Link
abilities.description: Creates a charged link between Razor and an enemy Hero, stealing damage from the target and giving it to Razor.

abilities.name: Unstable Current
abilities.description: Passively increases your movement speed and occasionally hits every unit in the area for some damage.

abilities.name: Eye of the Storm
abilities.description: A powerful lightning storm strikes out at enemy units with the lowest health, dealing damage and reducing their armor.  Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: -0.1 Eye of the Storm Strike Interval
-0.1 Eye of the Storm Strike Interval

abilities.name: Burrowstrike
abilities.description: Sand King burrows into the ground and tunnels forward, damaging and stunning enemy units above him as he resurfaces. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Sand Storm
abilities.description: Sand King creates a fearsome sandstorm that damages enemy units while hiding him from vision.  The effect ends when Sand King leaves the area.

abilities.name: Caustic Finale
abilities.description: Sand King's attacks inject a venom that causes enemy units to violently explode when its timer expires, or when the unit dies, damaging and slowing nearby enemies. Deals less damage if its timer expires.

abilities.name: Epicenter
abilities.description: CHANNELED - After channeling for 2 seconds, Sand King sends a disturbance into the earth, causing it to shudder violently. All enemies caught within range will take damage and become slowed. Each subsequent pulse increases the radius of damage dealt.

talents.name: 50% Sand Storm Slow and Blind
talents.description: Enemy units in range of Sand Storm have their movement speed slowed by %value%%% and miss %value%%% of their attacks.

abilities.name: Static Remnant
abilities.description: Creates an explosively charged image of Storm Spirit that lasts 12 seconds and will detonate and deal damage if an enemy unit comes near it.

abilities.name: Electric Vortex
abilities.description: A vortex that pulls an enemy unit to Storm Spirit's location. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Overload
abilities.description: Casting a spell creates an electrical charge, which is released in a burst on his next attack, dealing damage and slowing nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Ball Lightning
abilities.description: Storm Spirit becomes volatile electricity, charging across the battlefield until he depletes his mana or reaches his target. The activation mana cost is 30+8% of his total mana pool, and the cost per 100 units traveled is 12+0.7% of his total mana pool.  Damage is expressed in damage per 100 units traveled.

talents.name: 500 Distance Auto Remnant in Ball Lightning
talents.description: Every 500 distance travelled in Ball Lightning creates a Static Remnant.

talents.name: 500 Distance Auto Remnant in Ball Lightning

abilities.name: Storm Hammer
abilities.description: Sven unleashes his magical gauntlet that deals damage and stuns enemy units.

abilities.name: Great Cleave
abilities.description: Sven strikes with great force, cleaving all nearby enemy units with his attack.

abilities.name: Warcry
abilities.description: Sven's Warcry heartens his allied heroes for battle, increasing their movement speed and provides them with an attack damage shield. Buff ends if the shield is consumed. Shield health grows based on Sven's strength.

abilities.name: God's Strength
abilities.description: Sven channels his rogue strength, granting bonus damage for 25 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Storm Hammer Dispels Enemies
talents.description: Applies a basic dispel on all enemies hit.

abilities.name: Avalanche
abilities.description: Bombards an area with rocks, continously doing small intervals of damage and stun to enemy units. Avalanche does 3x damage to units being tossed.

abilities.name: Toss
abilities.description: Grabs the nearest unit in a 275 radius around Tiny, ally or enemy, and launches it at the target unit or rune to deal damage where they land.  If the tossed unit is an enemy, it will take an extra 30% damage.

abilities.name: Tree Grab
abilities.description: Grabs a tree to whack enemies on the head for a limited number of times. Grants bonus attack range. Attacks deal more damage (increased vs. buildings) and fully splash on units along the way. The tree can be thrown, expending all the charges, to deal your attack to a unit at a distance.

abilities.name: Grow
abilities.description: Tiny gains craggy mass, increases his power and causes him to shrug off debuffs.

abilities.name: Tree Throw
abilities.description: Consume the remaining Tree Grab charges and throws the tree at the target unit, proccing your attack on it and splashing damage around the target.

talents.name: Toss Requires No Target
talents.description: Toss can target the ground as well as enemy units.

abilities.name: Magic Missile
abilities.description: Fires a magic missile at an enemy unit, stunning and dealing damage.

abilities.name: Wave of Terror
abilities.description: Vengeful Spirit lets loose a wicked cry, weakening the armor of enemies and giving vision of the path ahead.

abilities.name: Vengeance Aura
abilities.description: Vengeful Spirit's presence increases the physical damage of nearby friendly units. Spawns a Vengeance Illusion when you die that lasts until you revive.

abilities.name: Nether Swap
abilities.description: Instantaneously swaps positions with a target Hero, friend or enemy.  Nether Swap interrupts channeling abilities on the target. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Shackleshot
abilities.description: Shackles the target to an enemy unit or tree in a line directly behind it.  If no unit or tree is present, the stun duration is reduced to 0.75.

abilities.name: Powershot
abilities.description: Windranger charges her bow for up to 1 second for a single powerful shot, which deals more damage the longer it is charged. The arrow damages enemies and destroys trees along its path. For each enemy that Powershot hits, its damage is reduced by 20%.

abilities.name: Windrun
abilities.description: Increases movement speed and adds evasion from all physical attacks, while slowing movement of nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Focus Fire
abilities.description: Windranger channels the wind to gain 425 additional attack speed against a single enemy unit or structure, though with a reduction to her attack damage.  Extra damage from secondary item effects is not reduced.  Lasts 20 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Arc Lightning
abilities.description: Hurls a bolt of lightning that leaps through nearby enemy units.

abilities.name: Lightning Bolt
abilities.description: Calls down a bolt of lightning to strike an enemy unit, causing damage and a mini-stun. When cast, Lightning Bolt briefly provides unobstructed vision and True Sight around the target in a 750 radius. Can be cast on the ground, affecting the closest enemy hero in 325 range.

abilities.name: Static Field
abilities.description: Zeus shocks any enemy hit by his abilities, causing damage proportional to their current health.

abilities.name: Nimbus
abilities.description: Creates a storm cloud anywhere on the map that automatically casts Lightning Bolt on nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Thundergod's Wrath
abilities.description: Strikes all enemy heroes with a bolt of lightning, no matter where they may be.  Thundergod's Wrath also provides True Sight around each hero struck.  If an enemy hero is invisible, it takes no damage, but the True Sight is still created at that hero's location.

abilities.name: Torrent
abilities.description: Summons a rising torrent that, after a short delay, hurls enemy units into the sky, stunning, dealing damage and slowing movement speed.

abilities.name: Tidebringer
abilities.description: Kunkka's legendary sword grants increased damage and cleaves a large area of effect in front of him for a single strike.

abilities.name: X Marks the Spot
abilities.description: Targets a friendly or enemy Hero, marks their position with an X, and returns them to it after several seconds.  Kunkka can trigger the return at any time during the duration. Lasts twice as long on allied heroes.

abilities.name: Ghostship
abilities.description: Summons a ghostly ship that sails through the battle before smashing apart, damaging and stunning all enemies caught near the wreckage. Allied heroes touched by the Ghostship are given a swig of The Admiral's Rum, receiving bonus movement speed and a delayed reaction to incoming damage. Upgradeable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Return
abilities.description: Returns the marked hero to the X.

talents.name: Ghostship Fleet
talents.description: Spawns 3 Ghostships, 2.8 seconds apart, towards the target location.

abilities.name: Dragon Slave
abilities.description: Lina channels the breath of a dragon, sending out a wave of fire that scorches every enemy in its path.

abilities.name: Light Strike Array
abilities.description: Summons a column of flames that damages and stuns enemies.

abilities.name: Fiery Soul
abilities.description: Grants bonus attack and movement speed each time Lina casts a spell. Stacks with itself. Lasts 10 seconds.

abilities.name: Laguna Blade
abilities.description: Fires off a bolt of lightning at a single enemy unit, dealing massive damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Earth Spike
abilities.description: Rock spikes burst from the earth along a straight path. Enemy units are hurled into the air, then are stunned and take damage when they fall.

abilities.name: Hex
abilities.description: Transforms an enemy unit into a harmless beast, with all special abilities disabled.

abilities.name: Mana Drain
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Absorbs the magical energies of a target enemy unit by taking mana from it every second.

abilities.name: Finger of Death
abilities.description: Rips at an enemy unit, trying to turn it inside-out. Deals massive damage and grows stronger with each life it consumes. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: +2 Mana Drain Multi Target
talents.description: Automatically targets additional enemy units with a mana pool within 400 distance around the original target.

abilities.name: Ether Shock
abilities.description: Creates a cone of ethereal energy that strikes multiple enemy units.

abilities.name: Hex
abilities.description: Transforms an enemy unit into a harmless creature, disabling their attacks and abilities.

abilities.name: Shackles
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Magically binds an enemy unit so that it cannot move or attack, while dealing damage over time.

abilities.name: Mass Serpent Ward
abilities.description: Summons 10 Serpent Wards to attack enemy units and structures. The Wards are immune to magic. It takes two hits to destroy a single Ward. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Guardian Sprint
abilities.description: Slardar slithers ahead, moving significantly faster and passing through units.  At ability level 4, Slardar may move at 700 speed while in the river.

abilities.name: Slithereen Crush
abilities.description: Slams the ground, stunning and damaging nearby enemy land units.  After the stun, the affected units are slowed.

abilities.name: Bash of the Deep
abilities.description: After 3 attacks, your next attack will bash the target.

abilities.name: Corrosive Haze
abilities.description: Reduces enemy armor to amplify physical damage and provides True Sight of the targeted unit, revealing invisibility.

abilities.name: Gush
abilities.description: Summons a gush of water to damage an enemy unit, reducing their movement speed and armor.  Lasts 4 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Kraken Shell
abilities.description: Thickens Tidehunter's hide to passively block a portion of any incoming physical attack damage. The hide also removes negative status effects if the damage taken crosses a threshold. Does not stack with items that provide Damage Block. DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

abilities.name: Anchor Smash
abilities.description: Tidehunter swings his mighty anchor to attack and deal bonus damage to nearby enemies and reduce their attack damage.

abilities.name: Ravage
abilities.description: Slams the ground, causing tentacles to erupt in all directions, damaging and stunning all nearby enemy units.

abilities.name: Paralyzing Cask
abilities.description: Launches a cask of paralyzing powder that ricochets between enemy units, stunning and damaging those it hits.

abilities.name: Voodoo Restoration
abilities.description: Witch Doctor focuses his magic to heal nearby allied units.

abilities.name: Maledict
abilities.description: Curses all enemy Heroes in a small area, causing them to take a set amount of damage each second, as well as bursts of damage every 4 seconds based on how much health they have lost since the curse began.

abilities.name: Death Ward
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Summons a deadly ward to attack enemy heroes within 700 range. Lasts a maximum of 8 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Frost Blast
abilities.description: Blasts the target enemy unit with damaging frost, dealing area damage and slowing movement and attack rates for 4 seconds.  The primary target takes the most damage.

abilities.name: Frost Shield
abilities.description: Applies a magical frost shield around you, reducing damage from attacks against you. While the shield is active, ice magic will be affect nearby enemy units every 1 seconds, doing minor damage and slowing.

abilities.name: Sinister Gaze
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Hypnotizes an enemy unit, causing it to move towards a point between the two of you.

abilities.name: Chain Frost
abilities.description: Releases an orb of frost that bounces between nearby enemy units up to 10/10/10 times, slowing and damaging each time it hits.  Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Attacks Apply 50% MS and AS Slow
Attacks Apply 50% MS and AS Slow

abilities.name: Smoke Screen
abilities.description: Throws down a smoke bomb, silencing enemies, and causing them to miss most attacks, as well as slowing movement.

abilities.name: Blink Strike
abilities.description: Teleports behind the target unit, striking for bonus damage if it is an enemy.

abilities.name: Cloak and Dagger
abilities.description: Riki fades into the shadows, becoming invisible. Every time Riki strikes his enemy from behind, he deals bonus damage based on his Agility. When Riki attacks, he becomes visible.

abilities.name: Tricks of the Trade
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Riki phases out of the world while striking random enemy heroes from behind in an area around him. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Cloak and Dagger Doesn't Reveal
talents.description: No actions take Riki out of invisibility, only revealed by sources of True Sight.

abilities.name: Malefice
abilities.description: Focuses Enigma's power on a target, causing it to take damage and become repeatedly stunned for multiple instances.  An instance strikes every 2 seconds.

abilities.name: Demonic Conversion
abilities.description: Transforms a creep into three fragments of Enigma himself.  These eidolons are all under Enigma's control, and repeated successful attacks cause them to multiply.  When this happens, the eidolons have their health restored.

abilities.name: Midnight Pulse
abilities.description: Steeps an area in dark resonance, damaging enemy units based on their max HP.

abilities.name: Black Hole
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Summons a vortex that sucks in nearby enemy units.  Enemies affected by Black Hole cannot move, attack, or cast spells. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Laser
abilities.description: Fires an intense energy beam, dealing damage and blinding the target, causing it to miss all physical attacks.  Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Heat-Seeking Missile
abilities.description: Launches a pair of rockets at the nearest visible enemy heroes within 2500 range.  Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: March of the Machines
abilities.description: Enlists an army of robotic minions to destroy enemy units in an area around Tinker.

abilities.name: Rearm
abilities.description: CHANNELED - Resets the cooldown on most of Tinker's items and abilities.

abilities.name: Shrapnel
abilities.description: Consumes a charge to launch a ball of shrapnel that showers the target area in explosive pellets. Enemies are subject to damage and slowed movement. Reveals the targeted area. Shrapnel charges restore every 50 seconds.

abilities.name: Headshot
abilities.description: Sniper increases his accuracy, giving him a chance to deal extra damage and briefly stop the movements of his enemies.

abilities.name: Take Aim
abilities.description: Extends the attack range of Sniper's rifle. Can be activated to double the attack range bonus for 1 attack.

abilities.name: Assassinate
abilities.description: Sniper locks onto a target enemy unit and, after a short aiming duration, fires a devastating shot that deals damage at long range and mini-stuns the target. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Death Pulse
abilities.description: Necrophos releases a wave of death around him, dealing damage to enemy units and healing allied units.

abilities.name: Ghost Shroud
abilities.description: Necrophos slips into the realm that separates the living from the dead. Unable to attack or be attacked, he emits an aura that slows enemies around him. He takes additional magic damage in this form, but his restorative powers are amplified.

abilities.name: Heartstopper Aura
abilities.description: Necrophos stills the hearts of his opponents, causing nearby enemy units to lose a percentage of their max health over time. Passively provides regen for 7 seconds for each unit Necrophos kills.

abilities.name: Reaper's Scythe
abilities.description: Stuns the target enemy hero, then deals damage based on how much life it is missing. Heroes killed by Reaper's Scythe will have 15/30/45 seconds added to their respawn timer. Any kill under this effect is credited to Necrophos. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Fatal Bonds
abilities.description: Binds several enemy units together, causing a percentage of the damage dealt to one of them to be felt by the others.

abilities.name: Shadow Word
abilities.description: Warlock whispers an incantation, healing a friendly unit or damaging an enemy unit over time.

abilities.name: Upheaval
abilities.description: CHANNELED - A powerful slowing current that grows stronger as it's channelled. Lasts up to 16 seconds.  Enemies are slowed for 3 seconds after leaving the area or the spell ends.

abilities.name: Chaotic Offering
abilities.description: Summons a Golem from the depths, stunning enemies for one second. The Golem lives 60 seconds, takes reduced damage from spells, has Permanent Immolation and Flaming Fists on attack. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Magic Immunity for Chaotic Offering Golems
Magic Immunity for Chaotic Offering Golems

abilities.name: Wild Axes
abilities.description: Beastmaster sends his axes flying and calls them home again, slicing through enemy units and trees along their path.  Each axe can hit an enemy once, and amplifies subsequent damage from Beastmaster and his units.

abilities.name: Call of the Wild Boar
abilities.description: Beastmaster calls forth a Boar to aid in the battlefield.

abilities.name: Call of the Wild Hawk
abilities.description: Beastmaster sends an invisible Hawk to scout an area.

abilities.name: Inner Beast
abilities.description: Untaps the inner fury of allies, passively increasing their attack speed.

abilities.name: Primal Roar
abilities.description: Beastmaster lets loose a deafening roar that stuns, and shoves open a path to its target. All units in the path of the roar are damaged, while units shoved aside by the roar have their movement and attack speed slowed. Additionally, Beastmaster and his units gain 40% movement speed for 3 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Shadow Strike
abilities.description: Hurls a poisoned dagger which deals large initial damage, and then deals damage over time. The poisoned unit has its movement speed slowed for 15 seconds.  An instance of damage is dealt every 3 seconds.

abilities.name: Blink
abilities.description: Short distance teleportation that allows Queen of Pain to move in and out of combat.

abilities.name: Scream Of Pain
abilities.description: The Queen of Pain lets loose a piercing scream around her, damaging nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Sonic Wave
abilities.description: Creates a gigantic wave of sound in front of Queen of Pain, dealing heavy damage to all enemy units in its wake and pushing them back. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Scream of Pain 1.5s Fear
talents.description: Enemies damaged by Scream of Pain are forced to run towards their fountain for 1.5 seconds.

abilities.name: Venomous Gale
abilities.description: Launches a ball of venom in a line, poisoning enemy units so that they take both initial damage and damage over time, as well as suffering slowed movement.  Venomous Gale deals damage every 3 seconds over its duration.

abilities.name: Poison Sting
abilities.description: Adds poison damage to Venomancer's normal attacks, slowing movement speed.

abilities.name: Plague Ward
abilities.description: Summons a plague ward to attack enemy units and structures. The ward is immune to magic. Wards gain the Poison Sting level from Venomancer, dealing 50% of the full damage.

abilities.name: Poison Nova
abilities.description: A spreading ring of poison that does damage over time to enemy units around Venomancer.  Poison Nova cannot deal lethal damage; targets will be left with at least 1 health. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Gale Hero Impact Summons 2 Wards
talents.description: The wards are based on the current level of Plague Ward and spawned within 100 range of the impacted Hero, on opposite sides.

abilities.name: Time Walk
abilities.description: Rushes to a target location while backtracking any damage taken the last 2 seconds.

abilities.name: Time Dilation
abilities.description: Faceless Void traps all nearby enemies in a time dilation field for 6/8/10/12 seconds, freezing their cooldowns and slowing their movement and attack speed by 14% for each cooldown frozen.

abilities.name: Time Lock
abilities.description: Adds the chance for an attack to lock an enemy unit in time while attacking it a second time.

abilities.name: Chronosphere
abilities.description: Creates a blister in spacetime, trapping all units caught in its sphere of influence and causes you to move very quickly inside it.  Only Faceless Void and any units he controls are unaffected.  Invisible units in the sphere will be revealed. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: +25% Backtrack
talents.description: Grants a %value%%% chance to avoid damage entirely.

abilities.name: Wraithfire Blast
abilities.description: Wraith King sears an enemy unit with spectral fire, dealing damage and stunning, then dealing damage over time and slowing the target.

abilities.name: Vampiric Aura
abilities.description: Nearby friendly melee units restore health based on the damage they deal when attacking enemy units.

abilities.name: Mortal Strike
abilities.description: Wraith King passively gains a chance to deal bonus damage on an attack. Every two kills on an enemy unit adds a skeleton charge. Skeletons respawn once when killed.

abilities.name: Reincarnation
abilities.description: Wraith King's form regroups after death, allowing him to resurrect when killed in battle.  Upon death, enemy units in a 900 radius will be slowed. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Reincarnation Casts Wraithfire Blast
talents.description: All enemy units within 900 range have the current level of Wraithfire Blast cast on them when Reincarnation triggers.

abilities.name: Crypt Swarm
abilities.description: Sends a swarm of winged beasts to savage enemy units in front of Death Prophet.

abilities.name: Silence
abilities.description: Prevents enemy units in a target area from casting spells.

abilities.name: Spirit Siphon
abilities.description: Creates a spirit link between Death Prophet and an enemy unit, draining 14 + 1/2.5/4/5.5% Max HP per second and steal %movement_slow%% movement speed from the enemy.

abilities.name: Exorcism
abilities.description: Unleashes evil spirits to drain the life of nearby enemy units and structures. At the end of the spell's duration, Death Prophet is healed in proportion to the damage dealt.  Lasts 35 seconds.

talents.name: Exorcism Grants Haste
talents.description: While Exorcism is active, Death Prophet moves at 550 movement speed and cannot be slowed.

abilities.name: Stifling Dagger
abilities.description: Throws a dagger slowing the enemy unit's movement speed, dealing 65+25/40/55/70% of Phantom Assassin's attack damage as physical damage and applying attack effects from items and abilities.

abilities.name: Phantom Strike
abilities.description: Teleports to a unit, friendly or enemy, and grants bonus attack speed while attacking if it's an enemy unit.

abilities.name: Blur
abilities.description: Phantom Assassin focuses inward, increasing her ability to evade enemy attacks. Can be activated to blur her body, causing her to be impossible to see until near enemy heroes. Stacks diminishingly with other sources of Evasion.

abilities.name: Coup de Grace
abilities.description: Phantom Assassin refines her combat abilities, gaining a chance of delivering a devastating critical strike to enemy units. Stifling Dagger shares the same critical strike chance.

talents.name: Triple Strike Stifling Dagger
talents.description: Launches a two extra Stifling Daggers towards random visible enemies within the cast range.

abilities.name: Nether Blast
abilities.description: An exploding pulse deals damage to enemies and structures in the area.  Deals half damage to structures.

abilities.name: Decrepify
abilities.description: A powerful banishing spell that slows a unit and renders it unable to attack or be attacked. Afflicted units take extra magic damage.

abilities.name: Nether Ward
abilities.description: Pugna places a Nether Ward at the target location. The ward reduces the mana regeneration of nearby enemy heroes, and will fire at any enemy hero who casts a spell. Nether Ward deals damage equal to the damage multiplier times the mana spent by the enemy hero.

abilities.name: Life Drain
abilities.description: CHANNELED - When cast on an enemy, Pugna drains health from the target enemy unit to heal himself and granting vision over the target. If Pugna has full HP, and the enemy target is a Hero, Life Drain will restore mana instead. When cast on an ally, Pugna will drain his own health into his ally. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Refraction
abilities.description: Templar Assassin becomes highly elusive, avoiding damage and gaining a bonus to her damage.  The damage and avoidance effects are separate, and have a limited number of instances.

abilities.name: Meld
abilities.description: Templar Assassin conceals herself, becoming invisible as long as she remains still.  If Meld's invisibility is broken by attacking an enemy, Lanaya will deal bonus damage to the enemy and reduce their armor for 10 seconds.

abilities.name: Psi Blades
abilities.description: Templar Assassin's psi blades slice through the attacked unit, splitting and damaging enemy units directly behind it, while gaining bonus attack range.

abilities.name: Trap
abilities.description: Springs the nearest trap, slowing nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Psionic Trap
abilities.description: Templar Assassin places mystical traps that invisibly monitor enemy movement. When sprung at her command, they exert a slowing influence of 30% in the area. Traps charge up to slow 60% after 4 seconds. Deals bonus damage when fully charged.

talents.name: Meld Dispels
talents.description: Applies a basic dispel to Templar Assassin.

abilities.name: Poison Attack
abilities.description: Intensifies Viper's venom, adding an effect to his normal attack that slows attack and movement speed while dealing damage over time based on how low the target is.

abilities.name: Nethertoxin
abilities.description: Viper releases a Nethertoxin at the targeted area. Units in that area take damage over time, have lower resistance and their passives do not work.

abilities.name: Corrosive Skin
abilities.description: Viper exudes an infectious toxin that damages and slows the attack speed of any enemy that damages it in a 1400 radius. The acid exudate also increases Viper's resistance to magic.

abilities.name: Viper Strike
abilities.description: Viper slows the targeted enemy unit's movement and attack speed while also dealing poison damage over time.  The slowing effect reduces over the duration of the poison. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Lucent Beam
abilities.description: Calls a beam of lunar energy down upon an enemy, damaging and briefly stunning them.

abilities.name: Moon Glaives
abilities.description: Empowers Luna's glaives, causing her attacks to bounce between enemy units. Deals less damage with each bounce.

abilities.name: Lunar Blessing
abilities.description: Increases the primary attribute for Luna and nearby allied heroes. Luna is also blessed with increased vision range at night.

abilities.name: Eclipse
abilities.description: Showers random nearby enemies with strikes from Luna's current level of Lucent Beam. These beams do not stun their targets, and there is a maximum number of times that a single target can be struck. Also turns day into night for 10 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Breathe Fire
abilities.description: Unleashes a breath of fire in front of Dragon Knight that burns enemies and reduces the damage their attacks deal.

abilities.name: Dragon Tail
abilities.description: Dragon Knight smites an enemy unit in melee range with his shield, stunning it while dealing minor damage.  When in Elder Dragon Form, the cast range increases to 400.

abilities.name: Dragon Blood
abilities.description: The life blood of the Dragon improves health regeneration and strengthens armor.

abilities.name: Elder Dragon Form
abilities.description:
Dragon Knight takes the form of one of three powerful elder dragons, increasing his speed, and Dragon Tail's range, while granting him new powers.
<font color="#9acd32">LEVEL 1 Green Dragon</font> - Corrosive Breath: attacks deal 20 poison damage per second for 5 seconds. Works on structures.
<font color="#ff0000">LEVEL 2 Red Dragon</font> - Splash Attack: attacks damage all enemy units in a 300 radius for 75% damage, with Corrosive Breath added to the targets.
<font color="#87ceeb">LEVEL 3 Blue Dragon</font> - Frost Breath: slows movement speed by 30% and attack speed by 30 of enemy units in Splash Attack range for 3 seconds, with Corrosive Breath added to the targets.

abilities.name: Poison Touch
abilities.description: Releases a cone of poison that strikes multiple enemy units. Deals damage over time and slows the targets. Anytime the targets get attacked, the debuff duration is refreshed.

abilities.name: Shallow Grave
abilities.description: An ally blessed with Shallow Grave, no matter how close to death, cannot die while under its protection. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Shadow Wave
abilities.description: Sends out a bolt of power that arcs between allies, healing them while damaging any units standing nearby.  Dazzle is always healed by Shadow Wave.

abilities.name: Bad Juju
abilities.description: Passively reduces cooldowns on your abilities and items. Anytime you cast a spell, all nearby enemies will have their armor reduced. Debuff stacks and refreshes duration.

abilities.name: Battery Assault
abilities.description: Discharges high-powered shrapnel at random nearby enemy units, dealing minor magical damage and ministun.

abilities.name: Power Cogs
abilities.description: Forms a barrier of energized cogs around Clockwerk, trapping any units that are near.  Enemies outside the trap that touch a cog are knocked back, losing health and mana. Once a cog has delivered a shock, it will power down.  Cogs can be destroyed by enemy attacks, but Clockwerk can destroy them with just one.

abilities.name: Rocket Flare
abilities.description: Fires a global range flare that explodes over a given area, damaging enemies and providing vision for 10 seconds.

abilities.name: Hookshot
abilities.description: Fires a grappling device rapidly at the target location.  If the hook hits a unit, Clockwerk launches himself into the target, stunning and dealing damage.  Any enemies Clockwerk collides with along the way are damaged and stunned. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Split Earth
abilities.description: Splits the earth under enemies. Deals damage and stuns for a short duration.

abilities.name: Diabolic Edict
abilities.description: Saturates the area around Leshrac with magical explosions that deal physical damage to enemy units and structures.  The fewer units available to attack, the more damage those units will take.  Deals 40% more damage to towers.  Lasts 10 seconds.

abilities.name: Lightning Storm
abilities.description: Summons a lightning storm that blasts the target enemy unit, then strikes any nearby enemy units. Struck enemies are slowed. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Pulse Nova
abilities.description: Creates waves of damaging energy around Leshrac, one per second, to damage nearby enemy units.

abilities.name: Sprout
abilities.description: Sprouts a ring of trees around a unit, trapping it in place.

abilities.name: Teleportation
abilities.description: Teleports to any point on the map.

abilities.name: Nature's Call
abilities.description: Converts an area of trees into Treants. Treants have 550 health and deal 27/30/33/36 damage.

abilities.name: Wrath of Nature
abilities.description: Damaging energy bounces around the map, striking enemies close to the cast point that are in vision. Each enemy hit beyond the first adds damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Rage
abilities.description: Launch into a maddened rage, becoming Spell Immune, 100% resistant to magic damage, and gaining increased attack speed. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

abilities.name: Feast
abilities.description: Lifestealer's attacks damage enemies and heal himself for a percentage of his target's max health.

abilities.name: Open Wounds
abilities.description: Lifestealer rends an enemy unit, slowing the victim's movement speed and allowing all allies to regain health for a percentage of the damage they deal to that unit. All damage dealt will steal life, including damage from spells. The victim recovers movement speed over the duration.

abilities.name: Assimilate
abilities.description: Lifestealer swallows an allied hero, allowing them to hide within him. Any healing Lifestealer receives is shared with the hero within. When an assimilated hero leaves Lifestealer, they erupt outward, damaging nearby enemies. DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

abilities.name: Infest
abilities.description: Lifestealer infests the body of a target unit, becoming undetectable inside. He can then explode from the host body, dealing damage to nearby enemies. If the infested unit is an enemy creep or a neutral creep, he can take control of the unit's ability to move and attack, and when consumed the creep will heal Lifestealer's health equal to the creep's current health.  Does not work on enemy heroes. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

abilities.name: Control
abilities.description: Lifestealer seizes control of the host body's nervous system, allowing him to issue movement and attack orders from within.  Controlled units share Lifestealer's movement speed.  Cannot be used on heroes.

abilities.name: Consume
abilities.description: Lifestealer eats the host body from the inside out, exploding from within.

abilities.name: Eject
abilities.description: Ejects an Assimilated hero, damaging nearby enemies.

abilities.name: Vacuum
abilities.description: Dark Seer creates a vacuum over the target area that sucks in enemy units, disrupting them and dealing damage.

abilities.name: Ion Shell
abilities.description: Surrounds the target unit with a bristling shield that damages enemy units in an area around it.

abilities.name: Surge
abilities.description: Charges a target friendly unit with power, giving it a brief burst of movement speed and removes unit collisions. Allows the unit to surpass the movement speed limit and cannot be slowed.

abilities.name: Wall of Replica
abilities.description: Raises a wall of warping light that slows and creates replicas of any enemy hero who crosses it. Enemy replicas serve at the Dark Seer's will. Replicas last until they are destroyed, or until the wall's duration ends. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Parallel Wall
talents.description: A second Wall of Replica is created 600 units behind the first wall.  Illusions are independent for each Wall.

abilities.name: Strafe
abilities.description: Clinkz nimbly attacks with a barrage of arrows. Dramatically increases attack speed for a short time and grants Clinkz the ability to automatically dodge projectiles.

abilities.name: Searing Arrows
abilities.description: Imbues Clinkz's arrows with fire for extra damage.

abilities.name: Skeleton Walk
abilities.description: Clinkz moves invisibly through units until the moment he attacks or uses an ability.

abilities.name: Burning Army
abilities.description: Clinkz summons an army of fiery ranged skeleton archers. Archers are immobile and die with 2 attacks from a hero. Skeletons use your current Searing Arrows ability and attack only heroes. Base damage is equal to your hero's base damage. Attack range is equal to your hero's attack range.

talents.name: Searing Arrows Multishot
talents.description: When using Searing Arrows, a second Searing Arrow targets a random enemy within the spell's range.

abilities.name: Purification
abilities.description: Instantly heals a friendly unit and damages all nearby enemy units.

abilities.name: Heavenly Grace
abilities.description: Creates a divine barrier around an ally which grants them increased Status Resistance, Strength and Health Regeneration. DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

abilities.name: Degen Aura
abilities.description: Greatly degenerates the movement and attack capabilities of enemy units that stray too near.

abilities.name: Guardian Angel
abilities.description: Omniknight summons a Guardian Angel that grants immunity from physical damage. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter

abilities.name: Untouchable
abilities.description: Enchantress beguiles her enemies, slowing their attacks when she is attacked.

abilities.name: Enchant
abilities.description: Enchantress charms an enemy. If the enemy is a hero, they are slowed. If the enemy is a creep, she brings it under her control. If cast on a creep already under her control, she refreshes its enchant duration. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

abilities.name: Nature's Attendants
abilities.description: A cloud of wisps heals Enchantress and any friendly units nearby. Lasts 11 seconds.

abilities.name: Impetus
abilities.description: Places an enchantment on each attack while activated, causing it to deal additional damage based on how far away the target is.  The farther the target, the greater the damage dealt. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Inner Fire
abilities.description: In a fiery rage, knocks all nearby enemies away from you to a fixed distance, dealing damage and disarming them.

abilities.name: Burning Spear
abilities.description: Huskar sets his spears aflame, dealing damage over time with his regular attack.  Multiple attacks will stack additional damage.  Each attack drains some of Huskar's health.  Lasts 8 seconds.

abilities.name: Berserker's Blood
abilities.description: Huskar's injuries feed his power, giving increased attack speed and health regen based on missing health. Health regen is a percentage of your strength.

abilities.name: Life Break
abilities.description: Huskar draws upon his health to break an enemy's life, leaping at a target within attack range to shatter a percentage of that hero's current health, and slowing them.  While leaping, Huskar is Spell Immune. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

talents.name: Burning Spears Pure Damage
talents.description: Pierces Spell Immunity.

abilities.name: Void
abilities.description: Creates a damaging void that slows an enemy unit and deals damage.  Void also mini-stuns, interrupting channeling abilities. The slowing effect lasts longer at night. Deals half damage during day.

abilities.name: Crippling Fear
abilities.description: Night Stalker horrifies all nearby enemies, causing them to become silenced while near him.  The effect lasts longer at night.

abilities.name: Hunter in the Night
abilities.description: Night Stalker is in his element at night, attacking and moving with great swiftness.

abilities.name: Dark Ascension
abilities.description: Night Stalker smothers the sun and summons instant darkness, so that he might use his powers at their fullest. Nightstalker gains flight and bonus damage during this time. Has unobstructed vision.

talents.name: +140 Hunter In The Night Attack Speed
+140 Hunter In The Night Attack Speed

abilities.name: Spawn Spiderlings
abilities.description: Broodmother injects her young into an enemy unit, dealing damage. The spiderlings will hatch if the target is killed while under this influence.

abilities.name: Spin Web
abilities.description: Spins a large web that grants Broodmother a passive movement speed increase, gives free movement, and boosts regeneration while in its vicinity. Spin Web charges restore every 45 seconds. Spin Web can be cast from anywhere as long as the new web touches an existing web. Webs never expire, and can be manually destroyed. When the maximum limit of webs is exceeded, the oldest web disappears.

abilities.name: Incapacitating Bite
abilities.description: Broodmother's venom cripples enemy units, causing her attacks to slow and giving the affected unit a chance to miss its attacks.

abilities.name: Insatiable Hunger
abilities.description: A violent lust for vital fluids increases Broodmother's attack damage and gives her a vampiric attack.

abilities.name: Shuriken Toss
abilities.description: Hurls a deadly shuriken at an enemy unit, dealing damage and mini-stunning the target.  The shuriken will bounce between any Tracked units who are within a 1200 radius of each other. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Jinada
abilities.description: Bounty Hunter plans his next hit, dealing bonus damage and stealing some unreliable gold.

abilities.name: Shadow Walk
abilities.description: Bounty Hunter becomes invisible and gains the ability to move through other units until he attacks or uses an ability.  If he breaks the invisibility with an attack, that attack will slow the target's movement speed.

abilities.name: Track
abilities.description: Tracks an enemy hero, granting True Sight of the target, and information on how much gold it is carrying. You move fast when near the tracked unit and deal critical strikes when attacking it. If the target dies, Bounty Hunter and nearby heroes collect a bonus bounty of gold. Casting Track does not take you out of invisibility.

abilities.name: The Swarm
abilities.description: Weaver launches a swarm of 12 young Weavers that latch on any enemy unit in their path, attacking and reducing armor until it is killed.

abilities.name: Shukuchi
abilities.description: Weaver shifts out of visibility, gaining the ability to move at maximum speed through physical units--doing harm to any enemies it passes through.

abilities.name: Geminate Attack
abilities.description: Allows Weaver to dispatch two attacks at once.

abilities.name: Time Lapse
abilities.description: Weaver warps backward to whatever position it was in five seconds earlier--regaining the HP and mana from that time. No effect on cooldown, gold or experience. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

abilities.name: Dual Breath
abilities.description: An icy blast followed by a wave of fire launches out in a path in front of Jakiro. The ice slows enemies, while the fire delivers damage over time.

abilities.name: Ice Path
abilities.description: Creates a path of ice that stuns and damages enemies that touch it.

abilities.name: Liquid Fire
abilities.description: Jakiro burns his enemies in an area of effect with fire added to his attack, while slowing their attacks.

abilities.name: Macropyre
abilities.description: Jakiro exhales a wide line of lasting flames, which deals damage per second to any enemy units caught in the fire. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Sticky Napalm
abilities.description: Drenches an area in sticky oil, amplifying damage from Batrider's attacks and abilities and slowing the movement speed and turn rate of enemies in the area.  Additional casts of Sticky Napalm continue to increase damage, up to 10 stacks.  The extra damage is halved against creeps.

abilities.name: Flamebreak
abilities.description: Hurls an explosive cocktail that explodes when it reaches the target location, knocking back, and dealing damage over time to enemies in the area.

abilities.name: Firefly
abilities.description: Batrider takes to the skies, laying down a trail of flames from the air.  The fire damages any enemies it touches, and destroys trees below Batrider. While flying, Batrider gains unobstructed movement and vision.

abilities.name: Flaming Lasso
abilities.description: Lassoes an enemy and drags them in Batrider's wake.  Victims cannot be dragged over impassable terrain. Dragged units cannot move, attack, or use abilities.  Teleporting or blinking will break the lasso. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Penitence
abilities.description: Forces an enemy unit to move slower and for allies to attack it more quickly.

abilities.name: Divine Favor
abilities.description: Provides increased health regeneration, amplifies all health restore by a percentage, and boosts damage. Provides triple bonus damage for non-hero targets.

abilities.name: Holy Persuasion
abilities.description: Chen takes control of an enemy or neutral creep. If the persuaded creep's base health is naturally below the health minimum, its base health will be raised to the health minimum. Can be cast on allies to teleport them to Chen. If cast on Chen, all units controlled by Chen will be teleported to him. Taking damage will dispel the buff.   Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Hand of God
abilities.description: Heals all allied heroes on the map as well as all units under Chen's control.

abilities.name: Test of Faith
abilities.description: Deals random damage to test an enemy unit's faith. Heals a random amount to allied units. Always applies the maximum effect when cast on yourself.

abilities.name: Spectral Dagger
abilities.description: Spectre flings a dagger to draw a Shadow Path, dealing damage and slowing the movement speed of any enemies along the trail. Units hit by the dagger also trail a Shadow Path. While treading the path, Spectre phases through otherwise impassable terrain.

abilities.name: Desolate
abilities.description: Deals bonus damage whenever Spectre attacks an enemy who is alone. Reduces the enemy vision for 5 seconds.

abilities.name: Dispersion
abilities.description: Damage done to Spectre is reflected on her enemies, leaving her unharmed. The effect lessens with distance.

abilities.name: Reality
abilities.description: Spectre exchanges places with a chosen Haunt.

abilities.name: Haunt
abilities.description: Creates a spectral nemesis to attack each enemy hero after a short delay. At any moment during the duration, Spectre can use Reality to exchange places of a given haunt. Haunt illusions are uncontrollable, take extra damage, and deal less damage than Spectre herself.  They move at 400 base movement speed and ignore terrain.

abilities.name: Cold Feet
abilities.description: Places a frozen hex on an enemy unit that deals damage over time, but can be dispelled by moving away from the initial cast point.  If the enemy unit doesn't move outside of the given range, it will be stunned and frozen in place after 4 seconds.

abilities.name: Ice Vortex
abilities.description: Creates a vortex of icy energy that slows movement speed and increases magic damage done in its range.

abilities.name: Chilling Touch
abilities.description: Enhances your attacks with heavy magic damage and slow. Grants increased range for this attack.

abilities.name: Ice Blast
abilities.description: Launches a tracer toward any location on the battlefield, which must be triggered again to mark the area to be blasted by a damaging explosion of hail. The further the tracer travels, the larger the explosion will be. Enemies caught in the explosion, or who touch the icy ball of hail as it travels, are Frostbitten, taking damage and prevented from regenerating or healing. If a Frostbitten unit's health drops below a certain percentage, they will instantly shatter. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Release
abilities.description: Releases the ice blast to explode at the tracer's current location.

abilities.name: Devour
abilities.description: Consumes an enemy or neutral creep, acquiring any special abilities that it possessed.

abilities.name: Scorched Earth
abilities.description: Carpets the nearby earth in flames which damage enemies, while also granting him increased movement speed.

abilities.name: Infernal Blade
abilities.description: Doom swings his burning sword, igniting the enemy. Stuns for 0.6 seconds and applies a 4 second burn that deals 25 + 1.25/2.5/3.75/5% of the target's Max HP as damage per second.

abilities.name: Devoured Ability
abilities.description: This slot will be replaced with abilities acquired using Devour.

abilities.name: Devoured Ability
abilities.description: This slot will be replaced with abilities acquired using Devour.

abilities.name: Doom
abilities.description: Inflicts a curse that prevents an enemy Hero from casting spells or using items, while taking damage over time. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

abilities.name: Earthshock
abilities.description: Ursa slams the earth, causing a powerful shock to damage and slow all enemy units in a nearby area for 4 seconds.

abilities.name: Overpower
abilities.description: Using his skill in combat, Ursa gains increased attack speed for a number of subsequent attacks.

abilities.name: Fury Swipes
abilities.description: Ursa's claws dig deeper wounds in the enemy, causing consecutive attacks to the same enemy to deal more damage.  If the same target is not attacked after 8/12/16/20 seconds, the bonus damage is lost.

abilities.name: Enrage
abilities.description: Ursa goes into a frenzy, multiplying his Fury Swipes damage and causing him to take 80% less damage. Removes any existing debuffs. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

abilities.name: Charge of Darkness
abilities.description: Spirit Breaker fixes his sight on an enemy unit and starts charging through all objects.  All enemy units passed through and the targeted unit will be hit by a Greater Bash.  If the targeted unit dies, Spirit Breaker will change his target to the nearest enemy unit to that location.

abilities.name: Bulldoze
abilities.description: Spirit Breaker gains movement speed and status resistance to ram through enemies. Can be used while charging.

abilities.name: Greater Bash
abilities.description: Gives a chance to stun and knockback an enemy unit on an attack, as well as gaining bonus movement speed after a bash occurs. Deals a percentage of movement speed as damage.

abilities.name: Nether Strike
abilities.description: Spirit Breaker slips into the nether realm, reappearing next to his hapless victim. Upon reappearing, a Greater Bash of the current level occurs and deals bonus damage. Knocks back for double the normal distance.  Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Rocket Barrage
abilities.description: Launches a salvo of rockets at nearby enemy units in a radius around the Gyrocopter.  Lasts 3 seconds.

abilities.name: Homing Missile
abilities.description: Fires a homing missile to seek the targeted enemy unit. The missile gains speed over time, dealing damage and stunning when it impacts the target. Enemy units can destroy the missile before it reaches its target.

abilities.name: Flak Cannon
abilities.description: Gyrocopter's attacks hit all enemy units in an area around it for a limited number of attacks.  Only the main target of attacks will receive attack bonuses such as Critical Strike.  Lasts 15 seconds or until the attacks are used.

abilities.name: Call Down
abilities.description: Call down an aerial missile strike on enemy units in a target area.  Two missiles arrive in succession, the first dealing major damage and minor slow for 2 seconds; the second dealing minor damage and major slow for 4 seconds. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Acid Spray
abilities.description: Sprays high-pressure acid across a target area. Enemy units who step across the contaminated terrain take damage per second and have their armor reduced.

abilities.name: Unstable Concoction
abilities.description: Alchemist brews up an unstable concoction that he can throw at an enemy hero, to stun and deal damage in an area around the explosion. The longer the concoction brews, the more damage it deals and the longer the stun. After 5 seconds, the brew reaches its maximum damage and stun time. However, after 5.5 seconds, the concoction will explode on Alchemist himself if not thrown.

abilities.name: Greevil's Greed
abilities.description: Alchemist synthesizes additional gold from his enemies and bounty runes. With each kill, Alchemist earns base bonus gold and extra bonus gold. If Alchemist kills another unit which yields gold within the next 40 seconds, an additional instance of Extra Bonus Gold is added to the total. Additionally, causes bounty runes to yield more gold.

abilities.name: Chemical Rage
abilities.description: Alchemist causes his Ogre to enter a chemically induced rage, reducing base attack cooldown and increasing movement speed and regeneration. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

abilities.name: Unstable Concoction Throw
abilities.description: Throw it before it blows up!

abilities.name: Arcane Curse
abilities.description: Curses the target area, causing enemy heroes to take damage and slowing their movement speed. Anytime affected enemies cast a spell, the duration is increased.

abilities.name: Glaives of Wisdom
abilities.description: Silencer enchants his glaives with his wisdom, dealing additional damage based on his Intelligence. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Last Word
abilities.description: Enchants a target, causing them to be damaged and silenced if they cast a spell or if the enchantment timer expires.

abilities.name: Global Silence
abilities.description: Silencer stops all sound, preventing enemy heroes and units on the map from casting spells.

abilities.name: Arcane Orb
abilities.description: Adds extra pure damage to Outworld Devourer's attacks, based on his remaining mana pool. Steals intelligence for 80 seconds per hit when attacking an enemy hero. Arcane Orb damage splashes in a small area.

abilities.name: Astral Imprisonment
abilities.description: Places a target unit into an astral prison. The hidden unit is invulnerable and disabled. When the astral prison implodes, it deals damage to the target and nearby enemies with 400 range. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Equilibrium
abilities.description: Causes any spell damage you deal to slow enemies and restore mana based on how much damage was dealt.

abilities.name: Sanity's Eclipse
abilities.description: Unleashes a psychic blast that removes 40% of the mana from affected heroes, while also damaging them based on the difference between the affected hero's Intelligence and Outworld Devourer's. If an enemy hero has the same or higher Intelligence than Outworld Devourer, Sanity's Eclipse will not cause damage. Sanity's Eclipse can hit units trapped by Astral Imprisonment.

abilities.name: Summon Wolves
abilities.description: Summons two wolves to fight for Lycan.  Level 3-4 wolves have Cripple, and level 4 wolves have permanent invisibility.

abilities.name: Howl
abilities.description: Grants bonus attack speed, armor, and health regen to Lycan, all allied heroes and all units under their control.

abilities.name: Feral Impulse
abilities.description: Increases the HP regeneration and damage of Lycan and all units under his control.

abilities.name: Shapeshift
abilities.description: Lycan assumes his lupine form, granting him and his units critical strikes and added vision at night. During Shapeshift, Lycan and all units under his control move at increased speed, cannot be slowed and have a 40% chance to deal a critical strike doing 150/175/200% damage.

abilities.name: Thunder Clap
abilities.description: Slams the ground, dealing damage and slowing the movement speed and attack rate of nearby enemy land units.

abilities.name: Cinder Brew
abilities.description: Drenches an area in alcohol, causing enemy units to have a chance to attack themselves, and combust whenever spell damage over 80 is dealt. Duration is refreshed when ignited.

abilities.name: Drunken Brawler
abilities.description: Goes into a drunken brawler state, granting you a chance to avoid attacks and to deal critical damage. Moves with a varying amount of movement speed, alternating between -20% slower and 40% faster. Lasts 5 seconds.

abilities.name: Primal Split
abilities.description: Splits Brewmaster into elements, forming 3 specialized warriors, adept at survival. If any of them survive until the end of their summoned timer, the Brewmaster is reborn. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Disruption
abilities.description: Banishes the targeted unit from the battlefield for a short duration.  Upon returning, two illusions of the banished unit are created under Shadow Demon's control.

abilities.name: Soul Catcher
abilities.description: Captures the soul of enemy units in an area, causing them to lose a percentage of their current health. When the debuff is removed, the units gain half of the lost health back. Units under the effect of Disruption can still be affected by Soul Catcher.

abilities.name: Shadow Poison
abilities.description: Deals damage in a line, and afflicts enemy units with a poison effect. The poison deals 1/2/4/8/16 times the stack damage based on the number of stacks on the target, up to 5 stacks. Additional stacks cause 50 damage each.  This deferred damage is dealt when Shadow Poison's duration is expired, or the Release sub-ability is used.

abilities.name: Shadow Poison Release
abilities.description: Releases the poison to do damage on all affected enemies. Units under the effect of Disruption can still be affected by Shadow Poison.

abilities.name: Demonic Purge
abilities.description: Purges the target enemy unit, removing positive buffs, and slowing the target for the duration.  The unit slowly regains its speed until the end of the duration, upon which damage is dealt.  Units under the effect of Disruption can still be affected by Demonic Purge. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter. DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

talents.name: Soul Catcher Creates Illusion On Death
Soul Catcher Creates Illusion On Death

abilities.name: Summon Spirit Bear
abilities.description: Summons a powerful Spirit Bear companion that can equip items.  If the bear moves 1100 distance away from the Lone Druid, it cannot attack.  Lone Druid suffers 10% of his max health as backlash damage if the Spirit Bear dies.  As the bear increases in levels, it can learn the Return, Entangling Claws, and Demolish abilities.  Spirit Bear does not benefit from attributes. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Spirit Link
abilities.description: Links Lone Druid and the Spirit Bear, increasing the attack speed of both and causing damage each one deals to heal the other.

abilities.name: Savage Roar
abilities.description: Lone Druid roars fiercely causing nearby enemies to flee towards their base in terror. Their movement speed is increased by 20%.

abilities.name: Battle Cry
abilities.description: Adds attack damage and armor to the Lone Druid as well as any nearby units under his control.

abilities.name: True Form
abilities.description: Lone Druid learns to morph himself into a raging bear, losing his ranged advantage and some base movement speed, but gaining melee power as well as the Battle Cry ability.  He can morph freely between druid and bear form. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Druid Form
abilities.description: Return to Druid form. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Chaos Bolt
abilities.description: Throws a mysterious bolt of energy at the target unit. It stuns for a random duration and deals random damage.

abilities.name: Reality Rift
abilities.description: Teleports you, any images you have and the target unit to a point along the line between the two of you. Slows the target's movement and attack speed.

abilities.name: Chaos Strike
abilities.description: Chaos Knight's attacks deal a critical strike of varying strength, in addition to a lifesteal for 25/40/55/70% of the damage.

abilities.name: Phantasm
abilities.description: Summons several phantasmal copies of the Chaos Knight from alternate dimensions. The phantasms deal 50/75/100% damage, but take 260% damage. Upgradeable by Aghanim's Scepter.\nDISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

abilities.name: Earthbind
abilities.description: Tosses a net at the target point, pinning down all enemy units.  Earthbind prevents invisibility and blink.

abilities.name: Poof
abilities.description: Drawing mystical energies from the earth, a Meepo can teleport to another Meepo or itself after channeling for 1.5 seconds, dealing damage in both the departure and arrival locations.

abilities.name: Ransack
abilities.description: Steals health from the enemy with each strike and heals all other Meepos for that amount.

abilities.name: Divided We Stand
abilities.description: Meepo summons an imperfect, semi-autonomous duplicate of himself, which can gain gold and experience as he does and shares his experience, attributes and abilities. However, the clones cannot wield any items but the boots that Meepo himself wears.  If any of the clones die, they all die. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Nature's Guise
abilities.description: Turns Treant invisible after a short delay when he is within close radius of a tree. Increases movement speed while invisible, and causes a disarming root when attacking out of invisibility.

abilities.name: Leech Seed
abilities.description: Treant plants a life-sapping seed in an enemy unit, draining its health, while simultaneously slowing it. The seed heals friendly units around it.  Pulses 7 times.

abilities.name: Living Armor
abilities.description: Infuses the target hero or structure with a protective coating which grants bonus regeneration. Also blocks some damage from all sources. Dispels when a number of damage instances are taken.

abilities.name: Eyes In The Forest
abilities.description: Treant Protector enchants a tree, which grants him unobstructed vision in that location. If Overgrowth is cast, units within a radius of an enchanted tree will be entangled and damaged.

abilities.name: Overgrowth
abilities.description: Summons an overgrowth of vines and branches around Treant that prevent afflicted enemies from moving, blinking, going invisible, or attacking.

talents.name: 2s Tree Respawn Time
talents.description: Any tree that is destroyed on the map will respawn 2 seconds later.

abilities.name: Fireblast
abilities.description: Blasts an enemy unit with a wave of fire, dealing damage and stunning the target.

abilities.name: Ignite
abilities.description: Drenches the target and another random unit in volatile chemicals, causing it to burst into flames. The target is in immense pain, taking damage and moving more slowly.

abilities.name: Bloodlust
abilities.description: Incites a frenzy in a friendly unit, increasing its movement speed and attack speed. Can be cast on towers.

abilities.name: Unrefined Fireblast
abilities.description: Blasts an enemy unit with a wave of fire, dealing damage and stunning the target. Its mana cost is 60% of Ogre Magi's current mana.

abilities.name: Multicast
abilities.description: Enables Ogre Magi to cast his abilities and items multiple times with each use.

abilities.name: Decay
abilities.description: Undying steals strength from all enemy heroes in an area, dealing base damage as he claims the enemy's strength for himself. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.

abilities.name: Soul Rip
abilities.description: Undying rips health away from all nearby units and uses it to heal an ally, or damage an enemy. Soul Rip can also be used to heal Tombstone.

abilities.name: Tombstone
abilities.description: Summons a tombstone at the target point.  Zombies will frequently spawn next to every enemy unit in the area around the Tombstone, and attack them.  Zombies have the Deathlust ability, which causes their attacks to slow the target, and if the target reaches below a certain amount of health, increases the attack and movement speed of the zombie.
